data.description: So much NEW, Why wait for new construction to be finished? All new kitchen appliances, paint, and flooring on the main floor with a newly finished basement. This spacious 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom home offers 2408 sqFeet of comfortable living space. The property boasts rich wood finishes in the kitchen with bright, clean finishes in the bathrooms, creating an inviting and elegant atmosphere.  The house features a bonus office/bedroom (unfinished)  space, perfect for those who work from home or need a quiet area to study. With its convenient location, this property is just a stone's throw away from schools. The insulated garage makes a great space for diy projects. The large backyard is a blank canvas waiting for a buyer to customize it be an escape from the day to day. Motivated Sellers!
